 is added to or withdrawn from therapy, and dosage adjustments made if necessary.', 'Metabolism', 'Concomitant use of pitolisant with other agents associated with QT interval prolongation should generally be avoided.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/141378/', '', 'Phenelzine, Tranylcypromine, Desvenlafaxine, Isocarboxazid, Oxitriptan, Tryptophan, Vortioxetine, Milnacipran, Levomilnacipran, Vilazodone, Esketamine', 'Dalfampridine, Inotersen, Riluzole, Tafamidis', 1767369485);
